$ SQLite: select statements
@ select statements

→ development/databases/SQLite/sql/select/join

→ development/databases/SQLite/sql/select/order-by[`order by`]

→ development/databases/SQLite/sql/analyze

→ development/databases/SQLite/sql/select/limit[limit clause] to select only the first n records or to page the result set.

The → development/databases/SQLite/shell[SQLite shell] command `.mode column` that allows to format a `select` result in → development/databases/SQLite/shell/tabular-output[tabular form].
